	* meson.build: Fix compatibility version on MacOS.

	Fixes #1117.

2021-11-21  Werner Lemberg  <wl@gnu.org>

	* src/truetype/ttinterp.c (Ins_MD): Avoid `FT_ABS`.

	Reported as

	  https://bugs.chromium.org/p/oss-fuzz/issues/detail?id=38562

